  "texts": [
    "One limitation of the analysis is that one cannot know what an executive refers to when they list \"artificial intelligence\" in their online profile.",
    "Therefore, we encourage future research to explore the breadth and depth of AI literacy of executives with more qualitative research designs.",
    "An executive-specific AI literacy taxonomy might pose a promising research direction with high practical relevance.",
    "Furthermore, such research could combine the role-oriented and skill-oriented perspectives on executives.",
    "Even though we emphasize the importance of the skill-oriented perspective in this study, executive roles are certainly still purposeful and will not vanish."
  ],
